import React, { useContext } from 'react'
import { Navbar, NavbarBrand, NavbarContent, NavbarItem, Text, NavbarLink } from '@nextui-org/react'

export const Header = () => {
    return (
        <Navbar isBordered variant={floating}>
        <NavbarBrand>
          <Text b color="inherit" hideIn="xs">
            ACME
          </Text>
        </NavbarBrand>
        <Navbar.Content hideIn="xs">
          <NavbarLink href="#">Features</NavbarLink>
          <NavbarLink isActive href="#">Customers</NavbarLink>
          <NavbarLink href="#">Pricing</NavbarLink>
          <NavbarLink href="#">Company</NavbarLink>
        </Navbar.Content>
        <Navbar.Content>
          <Navbar.Link color="inherit" href="#">
            Login
          </Navbar.Link>
          <Navbar.Item>
            <Button auto flat as={Link} href="#">
              Sign Up
            </Button>
          </Navbar.Item>
        </Navbar.Content>
      </Navbar>
    )
}
